{0 {e lua-re}: OCaml bindings for Lua 🌕️}

{b 🏚️ Homepage:} {:https://github.com/Nymphium/ocaml-lua-re}

{e lua-re} provides Lua bindings for OCaml using {{:https://github.com/yallop/ocaml-ctypes} ctypes}.

{[
Lua.run
@@ fun state ->
